      &lt;h2 class=&quot;my-0 mb-[16px] text-ellipsis text-[18px] font-medium text-emphasis&quot;&gt;
        延伸阅读
      &lt;/h2&gt;
      
          &lt;a referrer=&quot;null&quot; href=&quot;https://www.zaobao.com/news/china/story20250607-6609477&quot; target=&quot;_self&quot; class=&quot;title&quot; id=&quot;mobile-recommend-articles&quot;&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;my-0 line-clamp-4 leading-normal&quot;&gt;
              吉利董事长：汽车工业存在“严重的产能过剩”
