      &lt;/h2&gt;
      
          &lt;a referrer=&quot;null&quot; href=&quot;https://www.zaobao.com/news/china/story20250516-6400537&quot; target=&quot;_self&quot; class=&quot;title&quot; id=&quot;mobile-recommend-articles&quot;&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;my-0 line-clamp-4 leading-normal&quot;&gt;
              新任美驻华大使抵京  学者：与特朗普关系紧密或发挥桥梁作用
