            &lt;div class=&quot;relative min-w-[120px] w-[120px]&quot;&gt;
                    &lt;img alt=&quot;新任美驻华大使抵京  学者：与特朗普关系紧密或发挥桥梁作用&quot; title=&quot;新任美驻华大使抵京  学者：与特朗普关系紧密或发挥桥梁作用&quot; src=&quot;https://cassette.sphdigital.com.sg/image/zaobao/d20c1fb2a5bc2f37ebea8ea216f87500b6ec5c300cac37a49598b1b593af8e60&quot; class=&quot;my-0 w-full rounded-[4px] object-contain&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;
